DTSTAMP:20260709T211504Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260817
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260818
SUMMARY:Deadline: Copyright Agency Cultural Fund: Author Fellowship 2026
DESCRIPTION:The Copyright Agency Cultural Fund's Author Fellowship awards A
 UD 80\,000 to one established Australian author to create a significant ne
 w work for publication. ELIGIBILITY: established Australian authors with c
 ritical acclaim and confirmed publisher interest in the proposed work\; Au
 stralian residents only. This is a separate fellowship from the Cultural F
 und's Fellowship for Non-Fiction Writing\, though administered on the same
  cycle. APPLICATIONS close 17 August 2026\, 1:00pm AEST. Apply via the Cul
 tural Fund fellowship page.\n\nOrganisation: Copyright Agency (Cultural Fu
 nd)\nLocation: Australia\; Australian authors only.\nAward: AUD 80\,000 (o
 ne fellowship). No application fee.\nDuration: Fellowship to create a new 
 work\n\nMore: https://www.copyright.com.au/culturalfund/fellowship/?utm_so
