SUMMARY:Deadline: Club Nothing: Community Music Fund
DESCRIPTION:Club Nothing is a global events series and USD 40\,000 fund fro
 m the tech brand Nothing\, supporting organisers\, artists\, and collectiv
 es creating new music experiences. The fund will award four individuals or
  collectives USD 10\,000 each to throw a club event\, series\, or festival
  later this year\, backing disruptors bringing new sounds and experiences 
 to their communities through nightlife anywhere in the world. Applications
  are judged by a panel including DJ and producer Manuka Honey (Marissa Mal
 ik)\, Nothing Global Senior Community Manager and Madruga Festival co-foun
 der Erica Travis\, Nothing Global Head of Communications Shavone Charles\,
  Dazed Music Editor Solomon Pace-McCarrick\, A&R and music-publishing foun
 der James Supreme\, and music-industry professional Layla Mustafa Rock. Ap
 plications close 9 August 2026\; winners announced late August 2026. Learn
  more and apply at nothing.tech/club-nothing (details also posted at https
 ://nothing.community/d/59214-want-10000-to-throw-a-party). See full terms 
 at nothing.tech/club-nothing/terms-and-conditions.\n\nOrganisation: Nothin
 g\nLocation: Anywhere in the world.\nAward: USD 40\,000 fund total\; four 
 individuals or collectives each receive USD 10\,000 to produce a club even
 t\, series\, or festival. No application fee.\nDuration: Event\, series\, 
 or festival to take place later in 2026\; winners announced late August 20
 26.\n\nMore: https://nothing.tech/club-nothing?utm_source=artificialnouvea
 ugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
URL:https://nothing.tech/club-nothing?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk
 &utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:Anywhere in the world.
END:VEVENT
