 dios and cultural institutions positioned professionally in digital cultur
 e. Solo projects can receive EUR 10\,000-25\,000\; collaborative projects 
 with partners can receive up to EUR 50\,000. At least 20 percent of total 
 project costs must be covered by co-financing. Applicants must be register
 ed with the Dutch Chamber of Commerce (KvK). The 2026 application window f
 or this round runs 12-19 August 2026 (opens 12 August 15:00\, closes 19 Au
 gust 16:00 CEST)\; in 2026 the scheme runs only two rounds and this is the
