 tion: Stimuleringsfonds Creatieve Industrie (Creative Industries Fund NL)\
 nLocation: Netherlands. Requires Dutch Chamber of Commerce (KvK) registrat
 ion.\nAward: EUR 10\,000-25\,000 for solo projects\; EUR 10\,000-50\,000 f
 or collaborative projects with partners. At least 20 percent of total proj
 ect costs must be covered by co-financing. No application fee.\nDuration: 
 Project-based.\n\nMore: https://www.stimuleringsfonds.nl/en/grants/digital
