UID:casa-pip-residency-filmmakers-2026@artificialnouveau.github.io
DTSTAMP:20260709T211504Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260731
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260801
SUMMARY:Deadline: CASA PIP Residency for Filmmakers
DESCRIPTION:CASA PIP is a residency program in Portugal founded and run by 
 filmmakers. It encourages residents to slow down and play\, providing film
 makers with the time\, peace\, space\, and general "rulelessness" to move 
 meaningfully forward on their work\, whether it is a whole project or just
  the budding idea for one. The residency is free to attend. ELIGIBILITY: o
 pen internationally to filmmakers. There is a EUR 35 application fee. Dead
 line: July 31\, 2026.\n\nOrganisation: CASA PIP\nLocation: Portugal\; open
  internationally to filmmakers.\nAward: Free residency (no cost to attend)
 \, offering time\, space\, and peace to work on a project or an early idea
 . A EUR 35 application fee applies.\nDuration: Residency\n\nMore: https://
 casapip.com/apply?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referra
 l
