 nd innovative cultural relations projects in Sub-Saharan Africa\, co-creat
 ed through equitable partnership and mutual dialogue. THEMES: arts\, creat
 ive industries\, digitalisation\, education\, gender\, heritage\, human ri
 ghts\, social inclusion\, sports\, sustainability\, tourism\, youth and mo
 re. STRUCTURE: each project must be jointly defined and co-developed by a 
