DESCRIPTION:The Omidyar Network Tech Journalism Fund offers rolling grants 
 of $5\,000-$25\,000 for technology journalism projects. Relevant for journ
 alists and media organizations investigating AI\, tech policy\, and AI's i
 mpacts on culture\, society\, and creative industries. Applications are ac
 cepted on a rolling basis through December 31\, 2026 — one of the few cu
